       " 'T1114': {'name': 'Email Collection',\n",
       "  'description': 'target user email to collect sensitive information. Emails contain sensitive data, including trade secrets or personal information, that prove valuable to . Emails also contain details of ongoing incident response operations, which allow to adjust their techniques in order to maintain persistence or evade defenses. collect or forward email from mail servers or clients.',\n",
